# Built assets — gitignored, NOT committed. Appsero's automatic wp.org release is
# OFF, so the deploy-org.yml workflow is the sole publisher: it runs `npm run
# build` in CI and the default 10up deploy ships the on-disk working tree (this
# untracked assets/build) to SVN, applying .distignore — like wedevs-project-
# manager ships its gitignored /views/assets/dist. NOTE: do NOT use 10up BUILD_DIR
# (it syncs the git-tracked set and would strip this untracked build).
assets/build/
